legacy.full_text: In #Sanya, you can delve into the love legend at Luhuitou Scenic Area, immerse yourself in the intangible cultural heritages of the Li ethnic group, and relive a historic chapter of Yazhou Ancient City. Let's take a #citywalk and embark on a cultural tour! #SanyaCulture 😍🌴 https://t.co/0g05zuPYdu

legacy.full_text: 🌞🌡️#MajorHeat, or #Dashu, the hottest period of summer, began on July 12 🔥🔥. Escape the sweltering weather at Linchunling Forest Park, Egret Park, Dong'an Wetland Park, and any of the other forest and wetland sites in #Sanya! 🌳🌿🌊#GreenSanya https://t.co/neb6khOd2N

legacy.full_text: Do you like cute little animals?🐾Here are some places in #Sanya where kids can get close to nature: the MGM Grand Sanya, the Luhuitou Park, and the Sanya Haichang Fantasy Town. Get ready to meet adorable animals like deer, cats, dolphins, parrots, and more!🐱🦌🐬🐦#GlamourSanya https://t.co/wHaX4Jpukm

legacy.full_text: City graffiti has a magical power that leaves a lasting impression. In #Sanya, #graffiti art pieces can be found in popular spots like Tianwan, Qingtang, Meilian villages and Tianya town. These vibrant artworks bring life to walls and attract many visitors!😍🎨#VisitSanya https://t.co/fl8CJmqrNj
